				this.protocolContent  = `<div class="WordSection1" style="layout-grid:15.6pt">
					<p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; color:28pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">《用户使用协议》</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">尊敬的用户：</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">特别</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">提示</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">您在使</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">用平台相关功能</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">(以下简称“</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">本</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">平台”)</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">时</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">请认真阅读本《</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">用户使用协议</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">》(以下简称“协议”)</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">确保您充分理解本协议中</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">的</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">条款。请您审慎阅读并选择接受或不接受本协议</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">内容</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">。您同意并点击</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">接受</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">本协议条款且完成</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">实名认证、电子签名</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">后</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">才能成为</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">本平台</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">的用户</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">并享受</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">平台提供的</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">各类服务。您的</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">接受协议、实名认证、电子签名、</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">使用等行为将视为同意接受本协议各项条款</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">及其</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">约束。若您不同意本协议</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">或对本协议中的条款存在疑问</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">请您立即停止</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">本系统相关功能</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">的</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">使用，请按照本协议的内容做出您认为适当的选择。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21.1pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">我司非常重视用户的隐私和个人信息保护，您在使用本平台提供的相关服务时，我司可能会收集和使用您</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">提供</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">的相关信息。本协议条款将详细说明在使用本产品相关服务时如何收集、使用、保存、共享和转让这些信息。</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">本协议条款是对用户相</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">关政策的</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">说明</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">许诺，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">请您务必仔细阅读</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; color:0pt"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">一、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">相关名词定义</span></h1><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">CA机构：</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">指获得《电子认证服务许可证》的数字证书签发机构。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">数字证书</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">：指由</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">国家认可的</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">具有权威性</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">、</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">可信性和公正性的第三</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">方电子</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">认证服务机构</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">(</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">以下简称</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">CA机构</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">)</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">签发的，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">包含数字证书使用者身份信息和公开密钥的电子文件。能够标识您的身份，用于网络系统登录身份认证及确保您使用数字证书进行签名的电子数据的真实性、完整性、机密性和抗抵赖性，当您通过身份</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">认证</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">后</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">，</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">将为您签发数字证书。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">电子签名：</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">指数据电文中以电子形式所含、所附用于识别签名人身份并表明签名人认可其中内容的数据。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">电子签名法律效力</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">：根据《中华人民共和国电子签名法》的规定“可靠的电子签名与手写签名或盖章具有同等法律效力”。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">生物特征</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">识别</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">可以让计算机利用人体所固有的生理特征(指纹、虹膜、面相、DNA等)或行为特征(步态、击键、书写习惯等)来进行个人身份</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">识别</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">的技术</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">原笔迹电子签名：</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">基于</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">重庆傲雄在线</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">信息技术有限公司</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">特有的专利技术，以手写的方式在各种触屏终端上签署的数据电文，数据电文中以电子形式所含、所附用于识别电子签名人身份并表明电子签名人认可其中内容的数据。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">电子认证服务提供者：</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">指向社会公众提供服务的依法设立的电子认证服务机构，为需要第三方认证的电子签名提供认证服务的机构(以下称为“电子认证服务机构”)。(来源《电子认证服务管理办法》)</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">实名认证机构</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">：是对用户资料真实性进行的一种验证审核的机构。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; color:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">去标识化处理：</span><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:10.5pt">就是个人信息的去标识化处理，依照《个人信息安全规范》，数据控制者在收集个人信息后，必须进行去标识化处理，即通过相应的特殊技术处理，使得单凭该个人信息无法准确定位到特定个人。同时，信息控制者还必须采取一系列管理措施，确保经过去标识化处理的个人信息与未经过去标识化处理的个人信息分开保存，同时在后续的个人信息处理过程中也不得再次识别特定个人。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; color:0pt"><span style="font-family:方正楷体简体; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">二